item.title: How can I get the latest source of Runescape
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

As far as I know, This is the latest release (803). You also want to get the latest client from here.
It is not for people that have little Java knowledge. There is probably going to be a lot of content that has not been added, and you’ll have to do that yourself.

If you want to get the source yourself, you have to get the runescape client and decompile it. It’s going to be obfuscated so you’re going to have to deal with that too. From there, you have to build the source around how the client works.
Afaik that’s how you do it. Unless there’s a way to literally steal the source.
